name: ONIMATA-13
description:
ZORUKI SERIES

Set of 3
1 of 3

ZORUKI is a group of thieves who survived the era by stealing from others and have nowhere to go. Their sleight of hands and extraordinary speed are the skills they are proud of.

---------------

ONIMATA PROJECT (オニマタ) is my visual storytelling project that felling stories about a group of demons who survived the post apocalyptic world which caused by the unknown organization.

ONI means demon in Japanese, and MATA means eye in Bahasa Indonesia.
